This bird-like mask is an creation of [[artifice|artificer]] designed to protect the user against airborne toxins. The mask's beak is lined with magical flowers that react to and purify noxious air before it passes through the beak. While wearing the mask, you have [[advantage]] to resist being poisoned or diseased from airborne sources.